ammos.name: Armor Piercing Rounds
ammos.tooltip: Increased damage to heavy builds, decreased damage to light builds

ammos.name: Standard Rounds
ammos.tooltip: The classics are classic for a reason. Delivers full direct damage to the target. Limited against heavily armored targets like hardsuits.

ammos.name: Electro Rounds
ammos.tooltip: Increases damage against hardsuits, turrets and agents who are stunned, blinded, or in digi-grenade fields. Decreases damage otherwise.

ammos.name: Explosive Rounds
ammos.tooltip: Slightly decreases damage, but causes a loud ear-ringing explosion and prevents revives.

ammos.name: Hollow Point Rounds
ammos.tooltip: Increased damage to light builds, decreased damage to heavy builds

ammos.name: Incendiary Rounds
ammos.tooltip: Some direct damage with heavy fire damage over time. Hardsuit pilots will take some fire damage.

ammos.name: Toxic Rounds
ammos.tooltip: Medium direct damage and some damage over time that prevents targets from healing to full health.
